        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
Whenever there’s a discussion of international brands, a variety of fashion and its belongings, you are welcome to pop culture. It’s a wide array of modern ethics transmitted via the mass media and aimed particularly at younger people. Many major brands such as Nike, promoted this culture worldwide and now we can’t ignore its domination on millenials in India. The entertainment industry plays a major role, since it is the place where pop is born. Of course I am talking about Michael Jackson, the king of pop. And here in India it is mass media. You know it when you come to the Internet, listen to music, watch television, app-gaming or go to a movie, concert or stage show. You know the artists, the actors and actresses, sports personalities and the games they play. Today, anything with a buzz is deemed pop culture. <br><br>
If a collection of thoughts, ideas, attitudes, perspectives, images preferred by the mainstream population, say thanks to OTT platforms and Instagram. A huge group is fascinated by the stories and ideas that anything related to their favourite one becomes a culture. They hear what is in trend, they follow what they like and if mentality is same then it’s a pop culture. One can find a huge fan base of Avengers and Game of Thrones here, even a late 90’s shows such as FRIENDS is a sensation among the youth of India. <br><br>
In the late 80’s when the pop culture is introduced in the form of music, the community which welcomes it freehandedly were hipsters. Similar pattern can be observed in the Indian music industry. With the introduction of variety of local music and new artists and somehow the change of taste in the new genres, the pop culture is now much popular than the major music labels. The new artists have a huge fan base, such as Prateek Kuhad, Ankur Tiwari and bands like The Local Train got millions of views. Talking of this we get another source of pop culture, Youtube, yes it is that platform, which can be reached to anyone anywhere on this planet and with that the trends also travel. Major genre’s of music such as indie and pop gain popularity via Youtube. <br><br>
Today, the country has a large base of young population and they are the one who changes trends, in fact cultures are determined by the interests they poses, so what is pop here.
